.TH HISTCLEAN 1 2026-06-15 "" "General Commands Manual"
.SH NAME
histclean \- deduplicate shell history files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B histclean
.RB [ options ]
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.TP
.BR \-d ", " \-\-dry-run
Print deduplicated history to stdout without modifying the file.
.TP
.BR \-b ", " \-\-backup
Create a .backup copy before modifying.
.TP
.BR \-i ", " \-\-input " \fIfile\fP"
Read from
.I file
instead of the default.
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-output " \fIfile\fP"
Write to
.I file
instead of overwriting the input.
